      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
