    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E46 M3, presented in absolute concours condition. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with VAC coated bearings, and proactive bilateral subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis remains taut, riding on factory-spec suspension with refreshed bushings, while the variable M differential lock provides optimal torque vectoring. The exterior retains its factory-original depth and luster, free of rock chips or imperfections, matched by an interior with zero bolster wear or trim delamination. Documented with a meticulous service history, this is a mechanically flawless specimen for the purist who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
