    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been meticulously ceramic coated, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any UV fading or cracks. Every electronic feature, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a complete service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage remains spotless. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
